      "side": 1,
      "message": "The model for Monasca so far has been to fail on start-up if it can\u0027t initialize. So, while I agree adding the additional tests for connectionerror and connecttimeout might be good ideas, looping forever with a 10 second sleep in between is not so good. I would have exited with an error status code and let systemd or kubernetes handle restarting.",
