      "writtenOn": "2017-12-06T14:29:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How about sleeping 10s and then exiting with an error status code upon timeout? Otherwise monasca-api will restart a lot, potentially triggering a \"respawning too fast\" safety mechanism systemd, Kubernetes or Apache (depending on where it\u0027s run). For if there\u0027s a nontrivial number of agents using that monasca-api instance it is going to restart at a very high frequency.",
